{"tid":1907639,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31半周年荷籍男幼師涉燒垃圾桶 與同案男子今提堂不准保釋","createTime":"2020-03-02T17:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T22:44:19.000Z","uid":70063,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6df0ad5d9a95b72538fc478d4ac66c72631a17","tid":1907639,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"大批市民於上周六晚、即831半周年當天到太子站外擺放花壇悼念，惟因警方主動清拆站外花壇，再惹警民衝突。一名荷蘭籍幼兒教師與本地男子被指在旺角點燃紙張焚燒垃圾桶，被控一項縱火罪，今押解提堂。兩人申請保釋候訊均被拒，他們將於本月9日再出庭申請覆核擔保。<br />\n<br />\n被告鄧振強（42歲）及Edgar Willem Aart de Bruin（31歲），其中外籍男子為荷蘭籍，報稱任職教師，另據知鄧是採購經理。兩人共被控一項縱火罪，指他們於2月29日在旺角山東街與洗衣街交界，用火損壞香港政府的一個垃圾桶。<br />\n<br />\n控方申請暫不聽取答辯，以待警方進一步調查，包括檢驗兩人手提電話及翻看附近閉路電視片段。據知，控方指現場偵緝警長目擊兩人向路障加入火種，兩至三分鐘後一同離去，探員尾隨他們並截停查問，並將兩人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n辯方為二人申請保釋，但全遭主任裁判官羅德泉否決，須繼續還柙至4月27日再訊。據悉，荷蘭籍被告由中介聘用，來港教授幼稚園班級，現正透過僱主辦理工作簽證，目前以旅客身份逗留本港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200302/5WZZBBLN23JVNB555OLHZRVDUE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2F5WZZBBLN23JVNB555OLHZRVDUE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BBvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=402d85c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200302%2F5WZZBBLN23JVNB555OLHZRVDUE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=1a20e15d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200302/5WZZBBLN23JVNB555OLHZRVDUE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"bdd31a83dd0c9486d2ea23a92046ec9e60eda484","tid":1907639,"uid":64514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202